Installation note:
Unpack all files (EDoom_Movie01-18) into one drawer. Important!! make sure that you
unpack in the right order from file ...01 `til ....18. Don`t confuse the files the
installation won`t work.
After this double click on icon installanim
The whole installation needs around 100MB of harddisc space.

Important for gfx-board user!

To view the EvilsDoom intro movie please select a non gfx-board screen-
mode to play the movie correctly.
  
